# SDOC Documentation
{
    # Overview
    {
        SDOC ("Simple/Smart Documentation") is a plain text documentation format with explicit scoping. Documents are trees of nested scopes delimited by braces, with familiar inline formatting borrowed from Markdown.

        Use the sidebar to navigate. Shift+Click two docs to compare them side by side.
    }

